  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  subsort SpectecType < SpectecTypes .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  op syn-bool : -> SpectecType .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  op syn-nat : -> SpectecType .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
